{
  "stem": "311.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where they took us all to the concentration camp, to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The whole camp.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I remember, there was Berta, my-- my aunt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was a gorgeous, beautiful-- my young-- my youngest aunt and with-- going with the baby.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she didn't know what it-- you know, and everything, the tumult and everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she's got a seven-day-- a-- a two-week's old baby, you know, seven days after the bris, you know, wrapped up in a newspaper.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was holding, getting it all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Somebody told me that a woman came to-- [PHONE RINGING]",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somebody-- Close the door.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I came to-- to the ghetto, she was there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [NON-ENGLISH], you know, her husband, was there, which he was an accountant.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and we knew it, the way it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I said, what happened to the baby?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some woman, could have been my mother, took the baby from her and said, listen, take a rest, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll hold-- but the baby was crying.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they said, take a rest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'll hold the baby for you, you know, and everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Your mother said this to her sister?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't know if it was my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the way I heard, there was a woman came in and said, Berta, take a rest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'll hold the baby for you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, the baby was crying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was awful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a little boy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I heard that one of the Lithuanian soldiers grabbed the baby, you know, crying baby from her and hit it against the wall, smash-- smashed it against the wall.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Anyway-- or she saw it or she didn't see it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When she came to-- when we came back to-- took us to concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was an Arbeitslager Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
